### Subscription Service API Testing
### Use this file to test all CRUD operations

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5003
@authToken = your_admin_token_here

### ========================================
### SUBSCRIPTION PLAN CRUD OPERATIONS
### ========================================

### 1. Get All Subscription Plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 2. Get Subscription Plan by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 3. Create New Subscription Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Basic Plan Test",
    "description": "Basic subscription plan for testing",
    "price": 99.00,
    "duration": 30,
    "type": 1,
    "examCategory": "Engineering",
    "examId": 1,
    "features": ["Access to all mock tests", "Performance analytics", "Study materials"],
    "isActive": true,
    "sortOrder": 1,
    "translations": [
        {
            "languageCode": "hi",
            "name": "बेसिक प्लान टेस्ट",
            "description": "परीक्षण के लिए बेसिक सदस्यता योजना",
            "features": ["सभी मॉक टेस्ट तक पहुंच", "प्रदर्शन विश्लेषण", "अध्ययन सामग्री"]
        }
    ]
}

###

### 4. Update Subscription Plan
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Basic Plan",
    "description": "Updated basic subscription plan",
    "price": 149.00,
    "duration": 60,
    "type": 1,
    "examCategory": "Engineering",
    "examId": 1,
    "features": ["Updated features list", "New analytics", "Premium support"],
    "isActive": true,
    "sortOrder": 1
}

###

### 5. Delete Subscription Plan (Soft Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 6. Get Active Plans Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans/active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 7. Get Plans by Exam Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans/by-exam/Engineering
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 8. Get Plans by Exam ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans/by-exam-id/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### ========================================
### USER SUBSCRIPTION CRUD OPERATIONS  
### ========================================

### Variables for User Subscription
@userToken = your_user_token_here
@userId = 1
@planId = 1

### 9. Create User Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subscriptionPlanId": {{planId}},
    "razorpayOrderId": "order_test_123456",
    "autoRenew": true
}

###

### 10. Get User's Active Subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/my-subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 11. Get User Subscription History
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/history
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 12. Activate Subscription (After Payment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "razorpayOrderId": "order_test_123456",
    "razorpayPaymentId": "pay_test_789012",
    "razorpaySignature": "signature_test_345678"
}

###

### 13. Cancel User Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subscriptionId": 1,
    "cancellationReason": "No longer needed"
}

###

### ========================================
### ADMIN USER SUBSCRIPTION OPERATIONS
### ========================================

### 14. Get All User Subscriptions (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/user-subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 15. Get User Subscription History (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/user-subscriptions/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 16. Get Active Subscriptions (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/user-subscriptions/active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 17. Get Expiring Subscriptions (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/user-subscriptions/expiring?daysBeforeExpiry=7
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 18. Renew User Subscription (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/user-subscriptions/renew
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subscriptionId": 1,
    "autoRenew": true
}

###

### 19. Cancel User Subscription (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/user-subscriptions/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subscriptionId": 1,
    "cancellationReason": "Admin cancellation - testing"
}

###

### ========================================
### ERROR TESTING
### ========================================

### 20. Test Invalid Plan ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 21. Test Duplicate Plan Creation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Basic Plan Test",
    "description": "This should fail as duplicate",
    "price": 99.00,
    "duration": 30,
    "type": 1,
    "examCategory": "Engineering",
    "examId": 1,
    "features": ["Test features"],
    "isActive": true,
    "sortOrder": 1
}

###

### 22. Test Unauthorized Access
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/subscription-plans
# No Authorization header - should return 401

### ========================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ========================================

### 23. Service Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
# Or try the base URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/
